  "detailed_description": "Two teams of players face off in ZEscape, the multiplayer game that has you running for your life from the relentless forces of the undead!<br>Beat platforming challenges while defending and covering your teammates across challenging levels and bosses as the undead are chasing your delicious brains!<br>Make your escape or become one of them! ..BRAINS! Zombie multiplayer mayhem at it's best!<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br>-Fast-paced brain splashing, fire-cracking, gun packing asymmetric multiplayer action<br>-Zombie running and Survival game modes<br>-Realistic and unrealistic level designs<br>-Player gear customizations:<br><i>   -Hats<br>   -Sprays<br>   -Character Skins</i><br><br><strong>Class-based abilities:</strong><br><u>   Support</u><br><i>     -Healer<br>     -Ammo<br>     -Shield</i><br><u>    DMG</u><br><i>     -Fire<br>     -Water<br>     -Air</i><br><br>-Boss battles<br>-Server browser<br>-Dedicated servers<br>-Pancakes<br>-Good times<br>-A sense of humor<br><br>Connect with the developer and the ZEscape community on the official Discord!",
  "about_the_game": "Two teams of players face off in ZEscape, the multiplayer game that has you running for your life from the relentless forces of the undead!<br>Beat platforming challenges while defending and covering your teammates across challenging levels and bosses as the undead are chasing your delicious brains!<br>Make your escape or become one of them! ..BRAINS! Zombie multiplayer mayhem at it's best!<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br>-Fast-paced brain splashing, fire-cracking, gun packing asymmetric multiplayer action<br>-Zombie running and Survival game modes<br>-Realistic and unrealistic level designs<br>-Player gear customizations:<br><i>   -Hats<br>   -Sprays<br>   -Character Skins</i><br><br><strong>Class-based abilities:</strong><br><u>   Support</u><br><i>     -Healer<br>     -Ammo<br>     -Shield</i><br><u>    DMG</u><br><i>     -Fire<br>     -Water<br>     -Air</i><br><br>-Boss battles<br>-Server browser<br>-Dedicated servers<br>-Pancakes<br>-Good times<br>-A sense of humor<br><br>Connect with the developer and the ZEscape community on the official Discord!",
